    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then maybe also just ways"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1879980,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we're thinking about\nlike building this up"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1882200,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and continuing to\ndevelop new partnerships,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1885140,
    "dDurationMs": 3390,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "push the models towards\ngreater capabilities."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1888530,
    "dDurationMs": 4170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Where do you go when you start\nto think about the future?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1892700,
    "dDurationMs": 3180,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, so when we started\nto think about the future,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1895880,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, I think first\nwe need to make sure that"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1899720,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Claude has all of the\nfoundational knowledge"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1902450,
    "dDurationMs": 3450,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that any scientist in the\nbio world would have, right?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1905900,
    "dDurationMs": 3780,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So things like understanding\nprotein structural biology,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1909680,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "right?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1910513,
    "dDurationMs": 2737,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And being able to look at"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1913250,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a molecule from organic chemistry"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1915260,
    "dDurationMs": 1170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and understand its structure"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1916430,
    "dDurationMs": 1170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and function and things like that, right?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1917600,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so once you establish that base,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1919130,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "then I think there's some\nreally exciting places"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1921200,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we can go after that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1923120,
    "dDurationMs": 3030,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Where one of the ones that I really like"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1926150,
    "dDurationMs": 2850,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to talk about and that I think is critical"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1929000,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is Claude actually learning"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1930890,
    "dDurationMs": 3180,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to execute experiments in the lab, right?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1934070,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think in order to get\nto this world where,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1937220,
    "dDurationMs": 3750,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, we're all going,\nthat needs to happen."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1940970,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And again, this is a problem\nthat for so long, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1943970,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we've been making a lot of progress,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1945950,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "maybe not as much as some\nhad hoped for, right,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1947900,
    "dDurationMs": 3270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in terms of this vision of\nautomating the tedious work"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1951170,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of life in the lab."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1953690,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But I believe that it's possible now."
